#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.163"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.163:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.163:0.2"
msgid "17. Āghātavagga "
msgstr "17. Resentment "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: sākacchāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.163:0.3"
msgid "163. Sākacchasutta "
msgstr "163. Discussions "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.163:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There Venerable Sāriputta addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "an5.163:1.2"
msgid "“āvuso bhikkhave”ti. "
msgstr "“Reverends, mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.163:1.3"
msgid "“Āvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Reverend,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an5.163:1.4"
msgid "Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca: "
msgstr "Sāriputta said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.191, sc2
msgctxt "an5.163:2.1"
msgid "“Pañcahāvuso, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu alaṃ sākaccho sabrahmacārīnaṃ. "
msgstr "“A mendicant with five qualities is fit to hold a discussion with their spiritual companions. "

msgctxt "an5.163:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.163:2.3"
msgid "Idhāvuso, bhikkhu attanā ca sīlasampanno hoti, sīlasampadākathāya ca āgataṃ pañhaṃ byākattā hoti; "
msgstr "A mendicant is personally accomplished in ethics, and answers questions that come up when discussing accomplishment in ethics. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.163:2.4"
msgid "attanā ca samādhisampanno hoti, samādhisampadākathāya ca āgataṃ pañhaṃ byākattā hoti; "
msgstr "They’re personally accomplished in immersion, … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.163:2.5"
msgid "attanā ca paññāsampanno hoti, paññāsampadākathāya ca āgataṃ pañhaṃ byākattā hoti; "
msgstr "They’re personally accomplished in wisdom, … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.163:2.6"
msgid "attanā ca vimuttisampanno hoti, vimuttisampadākathāya ca āgataṃ pañhaṃ byākattā hoti; "
msgstr "They’re personally accomplished in freedom, … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.163:2.7"
msgid "attanā ca vimuttiñāṇadassanasampanno hoti, vimuttiñāṇadassanasampadākathāya ca āgataṃ pañhaṃ byākattā hoti. "
msgstr "They’re personally accomplished in the knowledge and vision of freedom, and they answer questions that come up when discussing accomplishment in the knowledge and vision of freedom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.163:2.8"
msgid "Imehi kho, āvuso, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu alaṃ sākaccho sabrahmacārīnan”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these five qualities is fit to hold a discussion with their spiritual companions.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.163:2.9"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
